2. Google Gemma-4 / Specialized Reconstructors

  - Usage: Gaming Industry and Sight Reconstruction.
  - Role: Gemma is used for Spatial Mapping and Image Return.
  - Function: In Gaming, Gemma takes the "Kinetic Tokens" from Nodes 17–26 and
